(1) Update Packages To Latest Version (Syntax)
----------------------------------------------

==> npm update Package_Name --save // Update Package.json Dependencies
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
EX: npm update gulp --save


==> npm update Package_Name // Update Package Globally
------------------------------------------------------
EX: npm update gulp


==> npm update --dev --save-dev // Update All Develpoment Dependencies


==> npm update // Update All Package.json Packages [Dependencies And devDependencies]


==> npm update -g // Update All Global Packages 


==> npm update -g Package_Name // Update Specific Package Globally
------------------------------------------------------------------
EX: npm update -g gulp


==> npm install npm@latest -g // Update NPM Globally 






